---
title: Barbecue Pulled Pork Sandwiches with Quick-Pickled Cucumbers and a Cabbage Carrot Slaw
description: If you think you have to spend hours by the barbecue pit to make pulled pork, think again. We’ve done the slow cooking for you—all you need to do is add some sauce and voila! These babies are done. But just because they’re fast doesn’t mean they’re lacking in finesse. In addition to the smoky and sweet flavors on the meat, there are crisp and crunchy quick-pickled cucumbers and a creamy cabbage and carrot slaw.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/barbecue-pulled-pork-sandwiches-3143eede.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/barbecue-pulled-pork-sandwiches-5a296a30a5ed1967dd007632-ea1e6a36.pdf
